00:15.146 --> 00:17.188
WHITE DRESS, PRINCE CHARMING,

00:17.188 --> 00:21.152
WHO'D CARRY YOU AWAY
TO A CASTLE ON A HILL.

00:21.152 --> 00:24.525
YOU'D LIE IN BED AT NIGHT
AND CLOSE YOUR EYES,

00:24.525 --> 00:27.198
