AND 32 CUPCAKES,

00:32.763 --> 00:34.535
AND THEY STILL DON'T
TASTE RIGHT.

00:34.535 --> 00:36.337
NO, THESE ARE GOOD.

00:36.337 --> 00:38.309
MARTHA STEWART
WOULD BE PROUD.

00:38.309 --> 00:39.710
YEAH, LOOK WHERE
IT GOT HER.

00:39.710 --> 00:44.075
SANTA CLAUS, THE TOOTH FAIRY,
PRINCE CHARMING --

00:44.075 --> 00:46.077
THEY WERE SO CLOSE,
YOU COULD TASTE THEM.

00:46.077 --> 00:49.049
THERE'S SOMETHING MISSING --
SOME SPECIFIC INGREDIENT.

00:49.049 --> 00:50.181
WHY CAN'T I REMEMBER?

00:50.181 --> 00:52.353
BUT EVENTUALLY YOU GROW UP.

00:52.353 --> 00:56.487
ONE DAY YOU OPEN YOUR EYES,

00:56.487 --> 00:59.160
LOOK, JUST CALL HER.
CALL YOUR MOTHER AND ASK.

00:59.160 --> 01:02.093
AND PEOPLE THEY CAN TRUST.

01:02.093 --> 01:03.664
I DON'T WANT
TO CALL MY MOTHER.

01:03.664 --> 01:06.767
â™ª BABY, DON'T YOU HEAR
