01:06.767 --> 01:09.340
SO, LET'S GO SLEEP
AT YOUR HOUSE TONIGHT.

01:09.340 --> 01:11.102
WHAT?

01:11.102 --> 01:12.803
WHY ARE WE ALWAYS SLEEPING
AT MY HOUSE?

01:12.803 --> 01:14.074
DO YOU EVEN HAVE ONE?

01:14.074 --> 01:15.146
ONE WHAT?

01:15.146 --> 01:17.678
A HOUSE.
WITH A CLOSET.

01:17.678 --> 01:21.312
WITH YOUR STUFF IN IT.
YOUR PERSONAL STUFF.

01:21.312 --> 01:23.284
DO YOU EVEN HAVE
ONE OF THOSE?

01:23.284 --> 01:26.157
MM.

01:26.157 --> 01:27.388
GOOD MORNING.

01:27.388 --> 01:29.520
HEY. YOU GUYS WANT
A CUPCAKE?

01:29.520 --> 01:31.622
IZZIE MADE 'EM.

01:31.622 --> 01:33.164
YOU KNOW, I LIKE IT HERE.

01:33.164 --> 01:34.325
HEY, YOU SAID SO YOURSELF --

01:34.325 --> 01:36.367
YOU LIKED HAVING
YOUR THINGS AROUND,

01:36.367 --> 01:38.129
SLEEPING IN YOUR OWN BED.

01:38.129 --> 01:40.271
YOU'RE LIKE A HEALTH NUT,
AREN'T YOU?

01:40.271 --> 01:44.135
YOU EAT MUESLI EVERY MORNING.

01:44.135 --> 01:45.836
NO, I DON'T.

01:45.836 --> 01:48.379
OKAY, THE MUESLI THING --
YOU DO.

01:48.379 --> 01:49.680
THE LAST 7 DAYS,
AT LEAST.

01:49.680 --> 01:51.382
OH, COME ON.

01:51.382 --> 01:54.215
I HAVEN'T BEEN HERE
FOR A WHOLE WEEK...

01:54.215 --> 01:56.287
HAVE I?

01:56.287 --> 02:00.151
SEE? EVEN THEY THINK
IT'S WEIRD.

02:00.151 --> 02:02.393
BUT THE THING IS,

02:02.393 --> 02:05.726
IT'S HARD TO LET GO
OF THAT FAIRY TALE ENTIRELY.

02:05.726 --> 02:09.460
ALMOST EVERYONE STILL HAS
THAT SMALLEST BIT OF HOPE --

02:09.460 --> 02:13.133
OF FAITH -- THAT ONE DAY
THEY'LL OPEN THEIR EYES

02:13.133 --> 02:16.667
AND IT WILL ALL COME TRUE.

02:18.169 --> 02:22.243
â™ª DAH-DAH DAH-DAH
DAH DAH DAH-DAH â™ª

02:23.844 --> 02:25.145
[ DOOR OPENS ]

02:25.145 --> 02:27.218
SO, I'VE CHECKED
THE SCHEDULE.

02:27.218 --> 02:28.579
I START E.N.T. ON THE 9th.

02:28.579 --> 02:29.720
IT'S A LIGHT ROTATION.

02:29.720 --> 02:31.151
CAN YOU GET ME IN THEN?

02:31.151 --> 02:33.554
OH, I'M AFRAID NOT.

02:33.554 --> 02:36.627
WE HAVE OPENINGS
ON THE 16th.

02:36.627 --> 02:40.791
THERE ARE OTHER OPTIONS
BESIDES TERMINATION, YOU KNOW?

02:40.791 --> 02:42.933
ADOPTION...

02:42.933 --> 02:45.296
KEEPING THE BABY.

02:45.296 --> 02:47.398
YOU THINK IT OVER.
CALL ME BACK.

02:47.398 --> 02:49.169
PUT ME DOWN FOR THE 16th.

02:49.169 --> 02:51.502
I'LL CONFIRM AFTER
I REARRANGE MY SCHEDULE.

02:51.502 --> 02:54.475
I KNOW THIS IS
A DIFFICULT DECISION.

02:54.475 --> 02:56.807
OKAY, YOU KNOW
THE TALKING PART?

02:56.807 --> 03:00.811
I'M NOT INTERESTED.

03:00.811 --> 03:03.714
SO, DEVO, YOU JUST HAD
A ROOT CANAL, CORRECT?

03:03.714 --> 03:04.855
YEAH.

03:04.855 --> 03:07.318
I COULDN'T STOP BLEEDING
AFTER -- LITERALLY.

03:07.318 --> 03:10.221
NOW I'M STUCK
WITH YOU GUYS.

03:10.221 --> 03:11.362
GIVE ME THE BULLET.

03:11.362 --> 03:12.363
17-YEAR-OLD FEMALE

03:12.363 --> 03:14.365
HOSPITALIZED
FOR EXCESSIVE BLEEDING,

03:14.365 --> 03:15.326
STATUS POST ROOT CANAL.

03:15.326 --> 03:17.368
ALSO HAD A SIGNIFICANT
NEW HEART MURMUR

03:17.368 --> 03:18.299
ASSOCIATED WITH FEVER.

03:18.299 --> 03:20.431
NOW AFEBRILE
ON ANTIBIOTICS.

03:20.431 --> 03:22.703
IF I'M GONNA DIE,
CAN YOU PAGE MY MOM AND DAD?

03:22.703 --> 03:24.605
YOU'RE NOT DYING.
WHERE ARE YOUR PARENTS?

03:24.605 --> 03:25.876
IN THE CAFETERIA.

03:25.876 --> 03:28.309
MY FREAK FATHER
LIKES HOSPITAL FOOD.

03:28.309 --> 03:29.640
YOU'RE IN EXCELLENT
HANDS HERE.

03:29.640 --> 03:32.212
DR. KAREV IS GONNA RUN
SOME LABS.

03:32.212 --> 03:33.884
AND I'LL SEE YOU
WITH YOUR PARENTS

03:33.884 --> 03:35.716
IN A LITTLE WHILE.

03:35.716 --> 03:37.848
ADD A BLEEDING TIME
TO THE COAGS.

03:37.848 --> 03:42.453
SO, WHAT KIND OF NAME
IS "DEVO," ANYWAY?

03:42.453 --> 03:44.224
'80s ROCKER.

03:44.224 --> 03:46.257
MY PARENTS DID
TOO MUCH BLOW.

03:46.257 --> 03:48.629
I CALL MYSELF "ESTHER."

03:48.629 --> 03:51.462
NICE SKIRT, ESTHER.
WHAT ARE YOU, AMISH?

03:51.462 --> 03:53.334
HAVEN'T YOU EVER SEEN
AN ORTHODOX JEW?

03:57.268 --> 03:58.809
THIS GUY BELONGS IN PSYCH.

03:58.809 --> 04:00.641
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
TURFING HIM HERE?

04:00.641 --> 04:01.672
HE'S MY GIFT TO YOU.

04:01.672 --> 04:03.013
HAD A SEIZURE TWO DAYS AGO

04:03.013 --> 04:04.315
AND ANOTHER ONE
THIS MORNING.

04:04.315 --> 04:05.776
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

04:05.776 --> 04:07.818
IT SAYS RIGHT HERE,
"HE TALKS TO DEAD PEOPLE,

04:07.818 --> 04:09.350
HIS FAMILY THINKS
HE'S DANGEROUS,

04:09.350 --> 04:10.681
AND THEY HAD HIM COMMITTED."

04:10.681 --> 04:12.553
THAT'S PSYCH, NOT NEURO.

04:12.553 --> 04:13.984
DIDN'T YOU GO TO MED SCHOOL?

04:13.984 --> 04:17.257
YES, UNLIKE THE CORRESPONDENCE
SCHOOL YOU ATTENDED.

04:17.257 --> 04:18.889
OH, THAT WOULD BE STANFORD,
RIGHT?

04:18.889 --> 04:20.561
I LEARNED NOT TO JUMP
TO CONCLUSIONS.

04:20.561 --> 04:21.732
SORRY, LADIES.

04:21.732 --> 04:23.564
WE CAN'T TAKE HIM BACK
UNTIL HE'S CLEARED.

04:23.564 --> 04:24.895
YOU'RE DUMPING HIM ON US?

04:24.895 --> 04:27.338
HE THINKS HIS SEIZURES
ARE VISIONS.

04:27.338 --> 04:28.499
HELLO!
THEY'RE NOT SEIZURES.

04:28.499 --> 04:29.700
I'M PSYCHIC.

04:29.700 --> 04:32.473
OF COURSE YOU ARE,
AND I'M A CHICKEN.

04:32.473 --> 04:34.274
HEY, GENIUS.

04:36.276 --> 04:37.478
OKAY, MR. DUFF.

04:37.478 --> 04:39.380
WE'RE GONNA START
OUR WORK-UP NOW.

04:39.380 --> 04:40.581
WORK ME UP, WORK ME DOWN.

04:40.581 --> 04:42.813
I'M TELLING YOU,
IT'S A WASTE OF TIME.

04:42.813 --> 04:44.455
CAN YOU GRIP
MY FINGERS, PLEASE?

04:51.492 --> 04:52.823
CRISTINA...

04:52.823 --> 04:54.695
MR. DUFF?

04:54.695 --> 04:56.667
MR. DUFF, ARE YOU OKAY?

04:58.899 --> 05:00.401
[ INHALES, EXHALES DEEPLY ]

05:00.401 --> 05:01.902
SOMEONE...

05:01.902 --> 05:04.405
SOMEONE WHAT?

05:04.405 --> 05:05.776
SOMEONE'S GONNA CHECK OUT.

05:05.776 --> 05:07.478
BYE-BYE.

05:07.478 --> 05:08.579
THE MAN -- HE'S NUTS.

05:08.579 --> 05:10.441
I'M DIZZY,
NOT DEAF, LADY.

05:10.441 --> 05:12.813
SOMEONE ON THE FOURTH FLOOR
IS GONNA DIE.

05:12.813 --> 05:14.485
Man:
Code blue, fourth floor.

05:14.485 --> 05:15.616
Code blue, fourth floor.

05:15.616 --> 05:17.388
Man: GOT A CODE.

05:17.388 --> 05:18.919
RIGHT AWAY.

05:18.919 --> 05:21.021
GET IT.

