THE FOURTH-FLOOR DEAD GUY.

06:14.575 --> 06:17.047
I NEED SOMEONE TO COVER ME
ON THE 16th. YOU IN?

06:17.047 --> 06:19.950
I'M THINKING ABOUT LETTING
MY HAIR GROW.

06:19.950 --> 06:23.614
AND MAYBE I WON'T SHAVE --
GO FOR THE STUBBLE EFFECT.

06:23.614 --> 06:25.385
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

06:25.385 --> 06:28.058
THE 16th, GEORGE.
CAN YOU COVER ME OR NOT?

06:28.058 --> 06:30.691
UH, YEAH. I GUESS.
WHY?

06:30.691 --> 06:33.424
IT'S NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

06:33.424 --> 06:36.096
A "THANK YOU" WOULD BE NICE.

06:36.096 --> 06:38.769
IT'S JUST THAT I HARDLY KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT YOU.

06:38.769 --> 06:40.901
I'M FROM NEW YORK.
I LIKE FERRY BOATS.

06:40.901 --> 06:43.504
ENOUGH WITH THE FERRY BOATS.
WHAT ABOUT YOUR FRIENDS?

06:43.504 --> 06:44.905
I'M A SURGEON.
I DON'T HAVE FRIENDS.

06:44.905 --> 06:46.837
EVERYBODY HAS FRIENDS.

06:46.837 --> 06:48.879
I MEAN, WHO DO YOU
HANG OUT WITH?

06:48.879 --> 06:50.641
WHAT DO YOU DO
ON YOUR DAYS OFF?

06:50.641 --> 06:52.012
THESE ARE IMPORTANT
QUESTIONS.

06:52.012 --> 06:53.644
AH, IMPORTANT FOR WHO?

06:53.644 --> 06:56.416
WE'RE HAVING SEX EVERY NIGHT.
I THINK I DESERVE DETAILS.

06:56.416 --> 06:57.918
YOU HAVE MORE DETAILS
THAN MOST.

06:57.918 --> 07:00.020
THIS IS GOING
SOMEWHERE WEIRD.

07:00.020 --> 07:01.922
I WANT FACTS,
AND UNTIL I GET THEM,

07:01.922 --> 07:03.894
MY PANTS ARE STAYING ON.

07:03.894 --> 07:05.926
OR YOU COULD JUST
ROLL WITH IT.

07:05.926 --> 07:07.998
BE FLEXIBLE.
SEE WHAT HAPPENS.

07:07.998 --> 07:09.159
I'M NOT FLEXIBLE.

07:09.159 --> 07:10.961
[ PAGER BEEPS ]

07:10.961 --> 07:11.962
THERE I DISAGREE.

07:11.962 --> 07:14.104
HMM. I GOT TO GO.

07:14.104 --> 07:15.566
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

07:17.568 --> 07:18.939
WE'LL FIND
THESE THINGS OUT.

07:18.939 --> 07:20.440
THAT'S THE FUN PART,
YOU KNOW?

07:20.440 --> 07:21.572
THAT'S THE GRAVY.

07:21.572 --> 07:23.073
THAT IS WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

07:23.073 --> 07:25.816
I DON'T WANT TO BE
YOUR GRAVY.

07:27.648 --> 07:29.780
[ SIGHS ]

07:29.780 --> 07:32.022
YOUR DAUGHTER NEEDS
A VALVE REPLACEMENT.

07:32.022 --> 07:34.184
TESTS ARE INDICATIVE
OF VON WILLEBRAND'S DISEASE,

07:34.184 --> 07:35.956
WHICH EXPLAINS
THE EXCESSIVE BLEEDING

07:35.956 --> 07:36.957
AFTER THE ROOT CANAL.

07:36.957 --> 07:38.088
AND THAT MEANS?

07:38.088 --> 07:40.531
DEVO CAN'T TAKE THE
BLOOD THINNERS NECESSARY

07:40.531 --> 07:42.032
TO MAINTAIN A MECHANICAL
HEART VALVE.

07:42.032 --> 07:44.495
WE'RE SUGGESTING
A PORCINE VALVE INSTEAD.

07:44.495 --> 07:45.896
PORCINE?

07:45.896 --> 07:47.197
AS IN PIG?

07:47.197 --> 07:50.100
IT'S THE STANDARD OF CARE
FOR SOMEONE IN THIS SITUATION.

07:50.100 --> 07:52.903
PIG, HUH?

07:52.903 --> 07:54.144
IT'S THE OTHER WHITE MEAT.

07:54.144 --> 07:57.948
I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU DO.
SAVE MY DAUGHTER'S LIFE.

07:57.948 --> 08:00.981
Woman:
Dr. Jennings to O.R. 7.

08:00.981 --> 08:03.083
Dr. Jennings to O.R. 7.

08:03.083 --> 08:04.615
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

08:04.615 --> 08:08.088
I'M REMOVING THE LUMP NOW.

08:08.088 --> 08:10.921
SOMEONE SAID YOU GUYS HAVE
A PSYCHIC RUNNING AROUND HERE.

08:10.921 --> 08:11.992
IS THAT TRUE?

08:11.992 --> 08:13.564
I DID NOT EVEN
HEAR YOU SAY THAT.

08:13.564 --> 08:16.527
PREDICTED SOMEONE WOULD DIE
ON THE FOURTH FLOOR.

08:16.527 --> 08:19.069
I.C.U.'s ON THE FOURTH FLOOR.
PEOPLE DIE ALL THE TIME.

08:19.069 --> 08:22.032
