UNTIL YOU GET TO MY THIGH.

08:45.095 --> 08:48.528
TRY WIGGLING YOUR TOES.

08:48.528 --> 08:50.200
ARE THEY MOVING?

08:50.200 --> 08:51.732
NO.

08:51.732 --> 08:53.163
DAMN.

08:53.163 --> 08:55.535
I COULD ABOUT
10 MINUTES AGO.

08:55.535 --> 08:57.768
WELL, YOUR SPINE X-RAYS
LOOK CLEAR.

08:57.768 --> 08:58.969
YOU FELL ROCK-CLIMBING?

08:58.969 --> 09:00.571
IN SNOHOMISH.
JUST A SMALL DROP.

09:00.571 --> 09:02.172
I WAS BELAYED.

09:02.172 --> 09:05.115
MY WIFE AND BOYS
ARE ON THE WAY.

09:05.115 --> 09:06.877
WHAT'S WRONG WITH ME,
ANYWAY?

09:06.877 --> 09:09.549
HOLD YOUR LEGS UP.

09:12.082 --> 09:13.553
SHOULD I BE SCARED NOW?

09:13.553 --> 09:15.626
JUST TRY AND RELAX.

09:15.626 --> 09:18.128
NURSE,
I NEED A STAT M.R.I.

09:18.128 --> 09:20.190
SEND AN INTERN WITH HIM.

09:20.190 --> 09:21.592
MAKE IT MEREDITH GREY.

09:21.592 --> 09:23.193
MM-HMM.

09:23.193 --> 09:25.235
Karev: EW --
THICK, SHORT NECK.

09:25.235 --> 09:27.167
THAT ISN'T GOOD.
IT'S HARD TO INTUBATE.

09:27.167 --> 09:28.198
YOU WANT ME TO DO THAT?

09:28.198 --> 09:30.170
HE'S MY PATIENT.
I'M FINE.

09:30.170 --> 09:32.943
I JUST CAN'T SEE ANYTHING.
ADD SUCTION.

09:35.005 --> 09:36.747
DON'T BREAK ANY TEETH.

09:36.747 --> 09:38.248
DON'T YOU THINK
I KNOW THAT?

09:41.682 --> 09:43.984
PULSE OX DOWN 87%.

09:43.984 --> 09:46.156
BAG HIM.

09:46.156 --> 09:48.088
ARE YOU SURE YOU DON'T
WANT ME TO DO THAT?

09:48.088 --> 09:49.820
NO, DAMN IT! TUBE.

09:49.820 --> 09:51.261
[ RAPID BEEPING ]

09:53.323 --> 09:55.866
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

09:55.866 --> 09:57.267
THERE.

09:57.267 --> 09:59.800
HUH. GOT IT.

10:02.873 --> 10:04.134
IT'S IN THE ESOPHAGUS.

10:04.134 --> 10:06.306
DON'T YOU KNOW AN ESOPHAGUS
FROM A TRACHEA?

10:06.306 --> 10:08.338
ANATOMY IS ALL MESSED UP
IN HERE.

10:08.338 --> 10:11.241
ARE YOU TRYING TO KILL
THIS PATIENT, O'MALLEY?

10:11.241 --> 10:14.885
MAYBE WE CAN SEND YOU BACK
TO PRACTICE ON MANNEQUINS.

10:14.885 --> 10:18.148
NO, IT'S JUST I HAVEN'T
DONE THIS MUCH.

10:18.148 --> 10:21.722
BUT WHEN I HAVE,
IT'S -- IT'S BEEN GOOD.

10:21.722 --> 10:25.025
IT'S JUST I-I HAVEN'T --

10:25.025 --> 10:27.397
LET'S REVIEW THE CONCEPTS.

10:27.397 --> 10:30.030
NEVER TAKE YOUR EYES AWAY.

10:30.030 --> 10:32.232
ALWAYS -- ALWAYS --
KNOW YOU CAN FOLLOW THROUGH.

10:32.232 --> 10:34.134
DON'T EVER FOLLOW THROUGH

10:34.134 --> 10:36.266
ON ONE OF MY PATIENTS,
O'MALLEY.

10:48.378 --> 10:51.782
BOTOX WOULD DO WONDERS
FOR ALL THOSE FROWN LINES.

10:51.782 --> 10:54.124
OKAY. SHUT UP.

10:54.124 --> 10:56.126
ARE YOU ALLOWED
TO TALK TO ME LIKE THAT?

10:56.126 --> 10:57.257
[ HISSES ]

10:57.257 --> 10:58.428
GOD, YOU'RE HOT...

10:58.428 --> 11:00.330
IN A MRS. LIVINGSTON
KIND OF WAY.

11:00.330 --> 11:02.993
SEE HERE?

11:02.993 --> 11:04.965
THESE ARE SPIKES
IN YOUR TEMPORAL LOBE.

11:04.965 --> 11:08.068
IT MEANS YOU HAVE EPILEPSY.
NOT VISIONS. SEIZURES.

11:08.068 --> 11:09.339
YOU THINK I'M EPILEPTIC?

11:09.339 --> 11:11.041
THAT IS SO NOT RIGHT.

11:11.041 --> 11:12.342
I'M GONNA ORDER AN M.R.I.

11:12.342 --> 11:14.304
SO I CAN TAKE A CLOSER LOOK
AT YOUR BRAIN.

11:14.304 --> 11:15.906
YEAH, THERE'S NO WAY --

11:19.209 --> 11:21.912
MR. DUFF?

11:21.912 --> 11:24.755
MR. DUFF, CAN YOU SEE ME?
CAN YOU HEAR ME?

11:24.755 --> 11:25.956
STAY WITH ME.

11:25.956 --> 11:27.217
I WOULDN'T HAVE PICKED YOU

11:27.217 --> 11:29.389
FOR THE MOMMY TRACK,
NURSE BETTY.

11:32.893 --> 11:34.765
SEE?

11:37.868 --> 11:40.070
I TOLD YOU
I KNOW THINGS.

11:40.070 --> 11:42.833
THIS PREGNANCY THING --
YOU CAN'T RUN AWAY FROM IT.

11:42.833 --> 11:47.778
â™ª SET YOURSELF A PLACE â™ª

11:47.778 --> 11:51.481
â™ª I WONDER IF YOU'LL
