11:51.481 --> 11:53.443
DR. BAILEY, I WANT OFF
THE PSYCHIC CASE.

11:53.443 --> 11:55.385
I'LL TAKE WHATEVER YOU GOT.
CAN I SWITCH?

11:55.385 --> 11:57.748
ASK NICELY.

11:57.748 --> 12:00.490
UH, WELL,
THIS IS ME DOING NICELY.

12:00.490 --> 12:02.022
LOOK, I KNOW THE TYPE.

