LET ME TAKE HIM.

12:05.295 --> 12:07.297
I DON'T DO SWITCHES.

12:07.297 --> 12:10.400
I'LL DO YOUR POST-OP NOTES
FOR A MONTH.

12:10.400 --> 12:12.302
FINE.
I CAN ACCEPT THAT.

12:12.302 --> 12:14.104
IZZIE, YOU GET PSYCH GUY.

12:14.104 --> 12:16.206
YAY.
THIS IS YOUR LUCKY DAY.

12:16.206 --> 12:18.138
YOU GET TO BE WITH ME
ON THE BREAST CANCER.

12:18.138 --> 12:20.170
THERE'S SPOTTING.
YOU'LL NEED TO DO A PELVIC.

12:20.170 --> 12:22.072
SHE'S PREGNANT.

12:36.226 --> 12:38.228
SEE? THIS.

12:38.228 --> 12:40.130
THE GUY'S FILMS ARE CLEAR.

12:40.130 --> 12:43.393
THERE'S NO REASON I CAN SEE
FOR HIS CREEPING PARALYSIS.

12:43.393 --> 12:45.335
IT'S JUST SO SURPRISING.

12:45.335 --> 12:47.767
I EXPECTED AN INTRUSION
INTO THE SPINAL SPACE

12:47.767 --> 12:49.840
OR A BONY SPUR
IN THE NUCLEUS PULPOSUS.

12:49.840 --> 12:51.141
WELL, YOU WERE WRONG.

12:51.141 --> 12:53.243
YOU DON'T ALWAYS GET
WHAT YOU EXPECT, DO YOU?

12:55.375 --> 12:57.107
WHAT IS YOUR PROBLEM?

12:57.107 --> 12:58.879
GIVE ME SOMETHING TO GO ON.

12:58.879 --> 13:00.180
ANYTHING.

13:00.180 --> 13:01.812
WHAT ARE YOUR
GRANDPARENTS' NAMES?

13:01.812 --> 13:03.113
I DON'T HAVE GRANDPARENTS.

13:03.113 --> 13:04.214
WHERE'D YOU GROW UP?

13:04.214 --> 13:05.785
WHAT'S YOUR FAVORITE
FLAVOR OF ICE CREAM?

13:05.785 --> 13:07.457
WHERE'D YOU SPEND
YOUR SUMMER VACATIONS?

13:07.457 --> 13:10.190
LIGHTEN UP -- IT'LL BE GOOD
FOR YOUR BLOOD PRESSURE.

13:10.190 --> 13:12.262
OH, DON'T YOU TELL ME
TO LIGHTEN UP.

13:12.262 --> 13:14.995
I'LL LIGHTEN UP WHEN I...

13:14.995 --> 13:17.167
FEEL LIGHT.

13:18.498 --> 13:20.570
DON'T WE HAVE
TREATMENT OPTIONS?

13:20.570 --> 13:22.903
I-I MEAN, AREN'T THERE
ALWAYS ALTERNATIVES?

13:22.903 --> 13:25.305
Yang: WITH THIS STAGE
OF INVASIVE CARCINOMA,

13:25.305 --> 13:27.137
SURGERY, CHEMO, RADIATION,

13:27.137 --> 13:29.109
AND DRUG THERAPY
ARE YOUR ONLY OPTIONS.

13:29.109 --> 13:31.141
CAN I WAIT UNTIL THE END
OF MY PREGNANCY?

13:31.141 --> 13:32.342
THE PREGNANCY HORMONES

13:32.342 --> 13:34.814
WILL LIKELY SPEED THE GROWTH
OF THE CANCER.

13:34.814 --> 13:35.846
AND THE BABY?

13:35.846 --> 13:37.417
NONE OF THESE COURSES
OF TREATMENT

13:37.417 --> 13:40.120
WILL ALLOW THE BABY TO SURVIVE.

13:40.120 --> 13:42.252
Wilson:
MR. AND MRS. GLASS,

13:42.252 --> 13:44.494
I UNDERSTAND
HOW DIFFICULT THIS IS.

13:44.494 --> 13:47.027
NO DISRESPECT,
BUT LIKE HELL YOU DO.

13:47.027 --> 13:50.230
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO MAKE
A DECISION

13:50.230 --> 13:52.232
AS TO HOW YOU WANT
TO PROCEED.

13:52.232 --> 13:54.164
YOU MEAN MY BABY'S LIFE
OR MY OWN?

13:55.265 --> 13:58.208
YES.

14:03.313 --> 14:06.616
WE'LL HAVE TO EVACUATE
THE FETUS.

14:09.319 --> 14:11.521
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

14:14.324 --> 14:16.026
Shepherd:
ANY CHANGES, MR. WALKER?

14:16.026 --> 14:18.128
Mr. Walker: I CAN'T MOVE
MY LEGS AT ALL NOW.

14:18.128 --> 14:19.990
HE WAS MOVING HIS LEGS
WHEN HE CAME IN.

14:19.990 --> 14:21.191
WHAT'S WRONG WITH HIM?

14:21.191 --> 14:22.432
I DON'T KNOW.

14:22.432 --> 14:24.294
THE PARALYSIS
IS MOVING QUICKLY,

14:24.294 --> 14:26.566
AND THERE WAS NOTHING
IN THE M.R.I. TO EXPLAIN IT.

14:26.566 --> 14:28.498
HAS TOMMY BEEN UNDER
ANY STRESS LATELY?

14:28.498 --> 14:30.470
YOU KNOW WHAT'S MAKING ME
STRESSED?

14:30.470 --> 14:32.472
BEING IN HERE
AND NOT BEING ABLE TO MOVE.

14:32.472 --> 14:35.375
DR. GREY...

14:35.375 --> 14:37.007
EMOTIONAL TRAUMA
CAN BE CONVERTED

14:37.007 --> 14:39.309
INTO SOMETHING PHYSICAL

14:39.309 --> 14:41.451
LIKE HYSTERICAL NUMBNESS
OR PARALYSIS.

14:41.451 --> 14:43.383
MAYBE THERE IS NO
PHYSIOLOGICAL REASON,

14:43.383 --> 14:45.415
AND HE'S JUST HAVING
A CONVERSION REACTION.

14:45.415 --> 14:46.516
IT'S PSYCHOSOMATIC?

14:46.516 --> 14:48.318
IT IS NOT
IN YOUR HEAD, MAN.

14:48.318 --> 14:49.459
I BELIEVE YOU.

14:49.459 --> 14:50.560
Stevens:
MR. DUFF, PLEASE.

14:53.093 --> 14:54.464
WHO WAS THAT?

14:54.464 --> 14:55.365
PSYCH SENT HIM DOWN.

14:55.365 --> 14:56.997
HE HAS VISIONS.

14:56.997 --> 14:59.329
IS THAT IT?
AM I CRAZY?

14:59.329 --> 15:01.401
NO. NO.

15:01.401 --> 15:04.434
I'M GONNA ORDER
A HIGHER-LEVEL M.R.I.

15:04.434 --> 15:06.406
WE'RE GONNA
FIGURE THIS OUT.

15:11.441 --> 15:13.483
YOU KNOW HOW IMPORTANT
THIS IS TO ME!

15:13.483 --> 15:15.015
THIS IS ABOUT SAVING
YOUR LIFE.

15:15.015 --> 15:17.587
YOU'RE NOT RESPECTING IT --
OR ME.

15:17.587 --> 15:19.349
YOU'RE LETTING THEM
PUT A PIG --

15:19.349 --> 15:21.251
A FREAKING NONKOSHER,
TRAIF MAMMAL --

15:21.251 --> 15:24.294
INTO MY CHEST --
INTO MY HEART --

15:24.294 --> 15:25.956
THE VERY ESSENCE
OF MY BEING!

15:25.956 --> 15:28.028
IT'S A PORCINE VALVE,
ACTUALLY.

15:28.028 --> 15:29.499
I DON'T CARE
WHAT THE HELL IT IS.

15:29.499 --> 15:31.561
IF YOU GIVE ME A PIG PART,
I MIGHT AS WELL BE DEAD.

15:31.561 --> 15:34.204
THIS ORTHODOX THING
WAS A MISTAKE.

15:34.204 --> 15:37.207
WHAT WAS WRONG WITH BEING
REFORM LIKE EVERYONE ELSE?

15:37.207 --> 15:39.509
YOU GUYS DON'T EVEN LIGHT
CANDLES FRIDAY NIGHTS.

15:39.509 --> 15:41.972
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
ALL THE PASSOVER PLAGUES.

15:41.972 --> 15:45.215
BOILS, VERMIN, PESTILENCE.
EVEN I KNOW THAT.

15:46.216 --> 15:47.477
MISS FRIEDMAN...

15:47.477 --> 15:50.680
I APPRECIATE YOUR EXTREME
RELIGIOUS CONVICTIONS.

15:50.680 --> 15:52.052
FIRE, HAIL...

15:52.052 --> 15:54.054
SIMPLY PUT,
WITHOUT THIS PROCEDURE,

15:54.054 --> 15:55.055
YOU WILL DIE.

15:56.686 --> 15:58.558
YOU'RE HOTSHOT DOCTORS.

15:58.558 --> 16:00.490
YOU'LL COME UP
WITH SOMETHING ELSE.

16:00.490 --> 16:03.393
AS LONG AS IT DOESN'T ANSWER
TO WILBUR AND SAY "OINK,"

16:03.393 --> 16:05.295
I DON'T CARE WHAT IT IS.

16:14.444 --> 16:17.307
YOUR NOSTRILS ARE FLARING.

16:17.307 --> 16:18.308
THEY ARE NOT.

16:18.308 --> 16:20.280
YOU'RE INTO ME.
I CAN TELL.

16:20.280 --> 16:22.252
DR. SMALL-AND-ANGRY
WAS A HOT APPETIZER,

16:22.252 --> 16:24.584
BUT YOU, DOC,
ARE A SMORGASBORD OF LUST.

16:24.584 --> 16:26.586
MR. DUFF, YOU'RE PRESSING
YOUR LUCK.

16:26.586 --> 16:29.119
WOULD YOU PRESS IT FOR ME?

16:29.119 --> 16:31.461
I HOPE YOU'RE NOT
CLAUSTROPHOBIC.

16:33.223 --> 16:35.465
YOU'RE STARING AT ME.
STOP IT.

16:35.465 --> 16:38.498
I'M LOOKING AT YOU,
BUT IT'S THE STRANGEST THING.

16:38.498 --> 16:40.630
I'M HUNGRY
FOR A CHOCOLATE CUPCAKE.

16:40.630 --> 16:42.232
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

16:42.232 --> 16:43.603
A CHOCOLATE CUPCAKE.

16:43.603 --> 16:45.305
MAYBE ONE OF THOSE
FUDGEY THINGS

16:45.305 --> 16:47.337
WITH THE WHITE SQUIGGLE
ON THE FROSTING.

16:47.337 --> 16:48.378
COULD YOU OBLIGE?

16:50.110 --> 16:52.682
WHAT, DO I STILL HAVE
SOME CHOCOLATE ON MY FACE

16:52.682 --> 16:54.584
OR IN MY HAIR
OR SOMETHING?

16:54.584 --> 16:56.086
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

16:56.086 --> 16:58.688
YOU. I KNOW THE DRILL,
SO KEEP IT UP.

16:58.688 --> 17:00.590
NEXT YOU'LL BE READING
MY CARDS,

17:00.590 --> 17:03.553
TELLING ME MY DEAD UNCLE
IS IN THE ROOM.

17:03.553 --> 17:04.554
IS HE?

17:04.554 --> 17:06.326
I DON'T HAVE A DEAD UNCLE.

17:06.326 --> 17:09.629
I'M WATCHING YOU.

17:14.464 --> 17:15.805
[ SNIFFS ]

17:18.138 --> 17:19.509
[ WHISTLING ]

17:22.072 --> 17:23.613
IF THAT'S TURKEY,
CAN I HAVE SOME?

17:23.613 --> 17:24.544
IT'S SOGGY.

17:24.544 --> 17:26.416
MAYBE IT'LL KILL YOU,
SOLVE EVERYTHING.

17:26.416 --> 17:27.747
I COULD HAVE GOTTEN THAT
INTUBATION.

17:27.747 --> 17:29.449
I AM GOOD AT INTUBATIONS.

17:29.449 --> 17:31.521
WHY DOES EVERYTHING
IN A HOSPITAL

17:31.521 --> 17:32.822
SMELL LIKE A HOSPITAL?

17:32.822 --> 17:35.485
DON'T BE SO HARD ON YOURSELF.
EVERYBODY MAKES MISTAKES.

17:35.485 --> 17:37.557
I'M GOOD AT A LOT
OF THINGS.

17:37.557 --> 17:39.489
Yang: HEY, GEORGE.
YOU NEED TO GET LAID.

17:39.489 --> 17:41.060
SEE THAT NURSE OVER THERE?

17:41.060 --> 17:43.193
SHE'S SINGLE.
SHE'S GOT RED HAIR.

17:43.193 --> 17:44.664
GO ASK HER OUT.

17:44.664 --> 17:46.596
I INTUBATED AN ESOPHAGUS.

17:46.596 --> 17:48.298
DUDE, YOU'RE TWEAKING.

17:48.298 --> 17:50.100
MAYBE YOU SHOULD GO SEE
THAT PSYCHIC.

17:50.100 --> 17:52.202
MR. DUFF IS NOT A PSYCHIC!

17:52.202 --> 17:53.543
I AM TRYING TO HELP YOU.

17:53.543 --> 17:55.074
GO BUY HER A LATTE

17:55.074 --> 17:57.607
AND FRESHEN UP
YOUR GONAD, PLEASE.

18:03.413 --> 18:04.654
SHUT UP.

18:04.654 --> 18:07.757
IT'S NOT TOO LATE
TO CALL HER.

18:07.757 --> 18:09.319
MOMS LIKE THAT --

18:09.319 --> 18:11.461
SURPRISES
ON THEIR BIRTHDAYS.

18:11.461 --> 18:14.794
YOU KNOW,
IT'S VERY HALLMARK.

18:21.801 --> 18:23.503
I'M 47, YOU KNOW?

18:23.503 --> 18:26.536
I'M 47 AND HAVING A BABY,
WHICH IS KIND OF A MIRACLE,

18:26.536 --> 18:29.639
AND IT KIND OF SUCKS,
IF YOU SEE WHAT I MEAN.

18:29.639 --> 18:31.110
[ SIGHS ]

18:31.110 --> 18:33.743
WE'D GIVEN UP ON THE KID THING
ABOUT A YEAR AGO.

18:33.743 --> 18:35.585
YOU KNOW,
FERTILITY TREATMENTS,

18:35.585 --> 18:37.887
ACUPUNCTURE NEEDLES
IN MY EYES.

18:37.887 --> 18:40.650
WELL, NOT REALLY,
BUT IT FELT LIKE IT.

18:40.650 --> 18:45.695
IT WAS LIKE, "SCREW THIS.
I WANT MY LIFE BACK."

18:45.695 --> 18:47.797
THEN ONE AWESOME NIGHT
ON THE BEACH

18:47.797 --> 18:49.659
WITH A BOTTLE OF MERLOT --

18:49.659 --> 18:51.831
I SHOULD HAVE THESE LABS BACK
IN A COUPLE HOURS.

18:51.831 --> 18:53.733
YOU GET IT, RIGHT?

18:53.733 --> 18:55.705
MY HESITATION?

18:55.705 --> 18:58.438
THIS ISN'T AN EASY DECISION,
I MEAN.

18:58.438 --> 18:59.769
I'M HAVING A BABY.

18:59.769 --> 19:03.273
YOU HAVE ADVANCED-STAGE
CARCINOMA.

19:03.273 --> 19:04.574
YOU'RE 47 YEARS OLD.

19:04.574 --> 19:07.577
STATISTICALLY YOU HAVE
A GOOD PROBABILITY OF SURVIVAL.

19:07.577 --> 19:08.918
IF YOU FOREGO TREATMENT,

19:08.918 --> 19:11.681
CHANCES ARE YOU WON'T SEE
YOUR BABY GO TO KINDERGARTEN,

19:11.681 --> 19:14.554
SO WHOSE LIFE ARE YOU
INTERESTED IN SAVING?

19:20.460 --> 19:21.761
EXCUSE ME.

19:27.667 --> 19:30.169
Mr. Walker: FIRST MY LEGS,
THEN MY STOMACH.

19:30.169 --> 19:31.170
GOD.

19:31.170 --> 19:32.472
DOC!

19:32.472 --> 19:34.544
DOC, MY HANDS CAN'T MOVE.

19:34.544 --> 19:35.745
SQUEEZE MY FINGERS.

19:35.745 --> 19:37.747
I CAN'T.

19:37.747 --> 19:39.709
RIGHT HERE. NO?

19:39.709 --> 19:42.482
LET ME KNOW
IF YOU FEEL THIS.

19:42.482 --> 19:43.883
HOW ABOUT THAT? HERE?

19:45.715 --> 19:47.957
ANYTHING HERE?
UP HERE? OKAY.

19:47.957 --> 19:49.589
NOTHING ON THIS SIDE?

19:49.589 --> 19:50.960
ALL RIGHT.
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

19:50.960 --> 19:52.722
CANCEL THE SECOND M.R.I.

19:52.722 --> 19:54.464
CALL DOWN AND PREP O.R. STAT.

19:54.464 --> 19:57.227
YOU'RE OPERATING?
ON WHAT?

19:57.227 --> 19:59.699
IF THERE WAS SOMETHING TO FIX,
WOULDN'T WE HAVE SEEN IT?

19:59.699 --> 20:02.472
I THINK THE M.R.I. MISSED
A CLOT IN HIS UPPER SPINE.

20:02.472 --> 20:04.304
I'M GONNA CUT HIM OPEN.
I'M GOING IN.

20:04.304 --> 20:05.805
WHAT IF YOU'RE WRONG?

20:05.805 --> 20:08.478
COULDN'T UNNECESSARY
SPINAL SURGERY DO MORE DAMAGE?

20:08.478 --> 20:10.240
IF WE WAIT ANY LONGER,

20:10.240 --> 20:12.442
WE HAVE A PARALYZED MAN
WHO CAN'T BREATHE.

20:12.442 --> 20:13.643
I'M TRUSTING MY INSTINCTS.

20:13.643 --> 20:16.646
SOMETIMES YOU GOT TO TAKE
A CHANCE TO SAVE A LIFE.

20:27.527 --> 20:32.262
â™ª WITH PHOTOGRAPHS â™ª

20:32.262 --> 20:35.865
YOUR MITRAL REGURGE
IS GETTING WORSE.

20:35.865 --> 20:38.608
THE VALVES ARE LEAKIER
THAN EVER.

20:41.941 --> 20:43.513
ARE YOU HITTING ON ME?

20:43.513 --> 20:45.515
IF YOU WANT ME TO.

20:45.515 --> 20:47.747
I HEAR THEY CALL YOU
DR. EVILSPAWN.

20:47.747 --> 20:49.649
WELL, ONLY THE PEOPLE
THAT LIKE ME.

20:49.649 --> 20:52.482
I GUESS THAT EXPLAINS
THE LACK-OF-FAITH THING.

20:52.482 --> 20:54.684
YOU KNOW, I KIND OF THINK
OF MYSELF AS A PAGAN,

20:54.684 --> 20:58.458
BUT, HEY, THAT'S JUST ME.

21:00.590 --> 21:04.364
YOU KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE
BEING A TEENAGER THESE DAYS?

21:04.364 --> 21:06.596
MY FRIENDS SPEND MOST
OF THEIR TIME SCREWING AROUND

21:06.596 --> 21:08.468
AND GETTING WASTED.

21:08.468 --> 21:10.540
AT LEAST I HAVE GOD.

21:10.540 --> 21:14.404
WELL, SO, GOD WANTS YOU
TO DIE, HUH?

21:14.404 --> 21:18.508
HE WANTS ME TO BE PASSIONATE
ABOUT WHAT I BELIEVE IN.

21:18.508 --> 21:20.009
YOU DON'T BELIEVE
IN ANYTHING.

21:20.009 --> 21:21.381
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

21:21.381 --> 21:23.483
MY MOTHER USED TO PRAY
TO SAINT JUDE FOR ME.

21:23.483 --> 21:25.455
HOW APPROPRIATE --

21:25.455 --> 21:27.587
PATRON SAINT
OF LOST CAUSES.

21:27.587 --> 21:28.758
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:28.758 --> 21:30.059
HMM.

21:36.065 --> 21:38.568
I DID AN ANGIO
ON MY PSYCH CASE.

21:38.568 --> 21:40.630
THE M.R.I. CAME OUT CLEAN,
BUT I SAW A DITZEL.

21:40.630 --> 21:42.672
THERE'S SOMETHING HERE.

21:42.672 --> 21:43.973
YEP, YOU'RE RIGHT.

21:43.973 --> 21:46.376
THERE'S AN A.V.M.
ON HIS LEFT TEMPORAL LOBE.

21:46.376 --> 21:48.578
I'LL SCHEDULE THE O.R.
FOR TONIGHT, THEN.

21:48.578 --> 21:49.579
BACK UP, GIRL.

21:49.579 --> 21:51.611
THERE'S HIGH RISK
OF SPONTANEOUS HEMORRHAGE.

21:51.611 --> 21:54.043
THE ATTENDING
HAS TO SEE THE FILMS.

21:54.043 --> 21:56.816
BELIEVE IT OR NOT, STEVENS,
WE HAVE TO FOLLOW PROTOCOL.

21:56.816 --> 21:58.788
BUT IF THE A.V.M.
LOOKS LIKE IT'S GONNA BLOW,

21:58.788 --> 21:59.949
WE FIX IT, RIGHT?

21:59.949 --> 22:02.892
IF THE MAN NEEDS TO BE FIXED,
WE'LL FIX HIM.

22:02.892 --> 22:04.594
WHY ARE YOU MOVING
SO QUICKLY?

22:04.594 --> 22:07.897
YOU GET TOO INVOLVED
WITH YOUR PATIENTS, IZZIE.

22:07.897 --> 22:09.859
WHY DO YOU MAKE EVERYTHING
SO PERSONAL?

22:09.859 --> 22:12.602
IT'S NOT PERSONAL.

22:13.703 --> 22:15.635
IT'S NOT.

22:18.538 --> 22:20.370
PULSE OX -- 98.

22:20.370 --> 22:22.412
WE'VE GOT TO SAVE
THIS CORD.

22:22.412 --> 22:25.074
THIS GUY'S BUILT LIKE
THE ROCK OF GIBRALTAR.

22:25.074 --> 22:26.546
YOU WANT ME TO START?

22:26.546 --> 22:27.577
I'M GONNA CUT HERE

22:27.577 --> 22:30.550
FROM THE BASE OF THE NECK
TO THE RIB CAGE.

22:30.550 --> 22:32.752
I WANT YOU TO HIT
THE BLEEDERS.

22:32.752 --> 22:35.725
I STILL DON'T THINK
WE SHOULD BE DOING THIS.

22:35.725 --> 22:38.728
THIS GUY HAS
A SPINAL HEMATOMA...

22:38.728 --> 22:41.461
WHICH LEFT UNTREATED
ARE ALMOST ALWAYS FATAL.

22:41.461 --> 22:42.662
YOU'RE CUTTING BLIND.

22:42.662 --> 22:44.834
WHATEVER HAPPENED
TO BEING PRACTICAL?

22:44.834 --> 22:46.836
I NEED TO INCREASE
MY FIELD OF VISION.

22:46.836 --> 22:48.698
USE A RETRACTOR.

22:48.698 --> 22:50.540
WOW.

22:50.540 --> 22:53.372
THE SPINE.

22:53.372 --> 22:55.144
THERE'S NO "WOW"
IN "PRACTICAL."

23:03.553 --> 23:06.686
WE HAVE DECIDED TO GO AHEAD
WITH THE EVACUATION.

23:06.686 --> 23:09.388
WHAT THE HELL, RIGHT?

23:09.388 --> 23:11.821
MAYBE THIS IS HOW
IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE.

23:11.821 --> 23:13.763
WE NEED TO START CHEMO
RIGHT AWAY, THEN.

23:13.763 --> 23:15.094
WE'LL GET EVERYTHING READY.

23:19.699 --> 23:21.671
HAVE YOU EVER DONE
A "D" AND "C" BEFORE?

23:21.671 --> 23:22.872
WE LEARNED AT SCHOOL.

23:22.872 --> 23:24.734
OKAY, UH, GO AHEAD.

23:24.734 --> 23:27.406
I'LL CALL AN O.B. RESIDENT
DOWN TO SUPERVISE.

23:27.406 --> 23:30.680
IF SHE NEEDS ANYTHING,
PAGE ME.

23:44.654 --> 23:47.426
Woman:
Dr. Grimm to I.C.U. stat.

23:47.426 --> 23:49.529
Dr. Grimm to I.C.U. stat.

23:49.529 --> 23:51.761
YOU'RE USING UP MY OXYGEN,
O'MALLEY.

23:51.761 --> 23:53.703
HOW DOES A POMPOUS,
COCKY JACKASS LIKE YOU

23:53.703 --> 23:56.536
ALWAYS HAVE WOMEN
ALL OVER HIM?

23:56.536 --> 23:59.539
LITTLE BLUE LOVE PILLS --
LOTS OF THEM.

23:59.539 --> 24:00.740
COME ON.

24:00.740 --> 24:01.711
[ SIGHS ]

24:01.711 --> 24:05.074
FLOAT LIKE A BUTTERFLY,
STING LIKE A BEE.

24:05.074 --> 24:08.918
THERE IT IS --
A BOVINE XENOGRAFT.

24:08.918 --> 24:10.149
HA HA HA HA!

24:12.181 --> 24:14.754
O'MALLEY,
YOU THINK TOO MUCH.

24:14.754 --> 24:15.885
CAN'T YOU SEE IT?

24:15.885 --> 24:17.186
YOU GOT TO DANCE AND JAB.

24:17.186 --> 24:20.189
DANCE AND JAB.
LIKE ME.

24:20.189 --> 24:21.891
I AM THE ALI OF THIS PLACE.

24:27.066 --> 24:30.069
[ PRAYING IN HEBREW ]

24:34.944 --> 24:36.806
[ KAREV COUGHS,
CLEARS THROAT ]

24:36.806 --> 24:39.749
DOES THE WALL EVER BOW BACK?

24:49.619 --> 24:51.861
IT'S CALLED DAVENING,
SMARTASS.

24:51.861 --> 24:54.163
THIS IS ME COMMUNING
WITH GOD,

24:54.163 --> 24:55.665
AND YOU'RE INTERRUPTING.

24:55.665 --> 24:58.027
I'VE FOUND
A TRANSPLANT OPTION.

24:58.027 --> 25:00.169
AT FIRST I THOUGHT MAYBE
A CADAVER,

25:00.169 --> 25:02.001
BUT THEY'RE REALLY HARD
TO FIND.

25:02.001 --> 25:05.004
AND THEN I REALIZED
DR. BURKE CAN TRANSPLANT

25:05.004 --> 25:08.177
A BOVINE MITRAL VALVE
INSTEAD OF THE PIG.

25:08.177 --> 25:09.779
SHE CAN GET A COW VALVE?

25:09.779 --> 25:12.281
DR. BURKE, WHY WASN'T THIS
MENTIONED BEFORE?

25:12.281 --> 25:15.745
THE BOVINE VALVE HAS ONLY BEEN
AN OPTION THE LAST FEW YEARS.

25:15.745 --> 25:17.787
AND IT'S A MUCH MORE
COMPLICATED PROCEDURE.

25:17.787 --> 25:20.750
BUT THE BEST PART IS
IT'S SUPERIOR TO THE PIG.

25:20.750 --> 25:21.791
IT LASTS LONGER.

25:23.653 --> 25:25.625
WHAT SMALL FRACTION
OF YOUR BRAIN

25:25.625 --> 25:27.026
WERE YOU USING IN THERE?

25:27.026 --> 25:28.227
CORRECT ME IF I'M WRONG,

25:28.227 --> 25:30.529
BUT DID YOU NOT PRESENT
AN ALTERNATIVE PROCEDURE

25:30.529 --> 25:32.061
WITHOUT CONSULTING
YOUR ATTENDING FIRST?

25:32.061 --> 25:33.132
I THOUGHT YOU'D BE --

25:33.132 --> 25:35.805
WHAT, IMPRESSED?
THAT'S JUST STUPID.

25:35.805 --> 25:37.607
WE'RE FINISHED HERE, KAREV.

25:37.607 --> 25:39.238
YOU'RE OFF THIS CASE.

25:53.082 --> 25:55.855
YOU NEED TO SIGN
THESE CONSENT FORMS

25:55.855 --> 25:57.957
SO WE CAN PROCEED
WITH YOUR SURGERY.

25:57.957 --> 26:00.860
I'M NOT SIGNING ANYTHING
UNLESS IT'S GOT MY NAME ON IT

26:00.860 --> 26:02.732
FOLLOWED BY
A WHOLE BUNCH OF ZEROS.

26:02.732 --> 26:04.293
LOOK, THE A.V.M. IS LOCATED

26:04.293 --> 26:05.965
IN THIS CRUCIAL PART
OF THE BRAIN.

26:05.965 --> 26:07.997
IT'S A TANGLE OF BLOOD VESSELS
THAT COULD BURST

26:07.997 --> 26:09.969
AND AFFECT YOUR SPEECH,
AMONG OTHER THINGS.

26:09.969 --> 26:12.001
WE KNOW YOUR VISIONS
ARE ACTUALLY SEIZURES.

26:12.001 --> 26:13.042
DO YOU?

26:13.042 --> 26:14.674
DO I WHAT?

26:14.674 --> 26:15.905
KNOW THEY'RE SEIZURES.

26:15.905 --> 26:18.307
YOU'RE REALLY GOOD
AT READING PEOPLE,

26:18.307 --> 26:19.308
AREN'T YOU,

26:19.308 --> 26:21.050
TELLING THEM
WHAT THEY WANT TO HEAR?

26:21.050 --> 26:23.012
THERE'S AN UNFORTUNATE
ALIGNMENT OF SATURN

26:23.012 --> 26:24.884
IN THE HOUSE OF JUPITER
RIGHT NOW.

26:24.884 --> 26:26.756
OKAY.

26:26.756 --> 26:28.758
I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

26:28.758 --> 26:31.360
YOU WATCH PEOPLE --
READ THEIR BODY LANGUAGE.

26:31.360 --> 26:33.893
YOU SAY "CHOCOLATE CUPCAKES,"
I LEAN TOWARDS YOU,

26:33.893 --> 26:35.795
SO YOU THINK YOU'RE
ON THE RIGHT TRACK.

26:35.795 --> 26:37.927
NOT ONLY DO YOU KNOW
YOU'RE HAVING SEIZURES,

26:37.927 --> 26:38.828
BUT YOU'RE MILKING IT.

26:38.828 --> 26:40.269
HMM.

26:40.269 --> 26:43.272
WELL, WE'LL JUST SEE
ABOUT THAT, CRICKET.

26:43.272 --> 26:45.805
WHAT?

26:45.805 --> 26:47.006
WHAT DID YOU JUST CALL ME?

26:47.006 --> 26:48.808
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:52.812 --> 26:54.283
I'M GONNA DO
A QUICK PELVIC EXAM.

26:54.283 --> 26:56.215
THE O.B. RESIDENT
SHOULD BE DOWN SOON.

26:56.215 --> 26:57.787
IT'S A SHORT PROCEDURE.

26:57.787 --> 26:59.248
YOUR HUSBAND CAN STAY
IF HE LIKES.

26:59.248 --> 27:00.920
WE CHANGED OUR MINDS.

27:00.920 --> 27:01.991
EXCUSE ME?

27:01.991 --> 27:03.622
WE'VE DECIDED
TO KEEP THE BABY.

27:03.622 --> 27:06.225
YOU HAVE CANCER.

27:06.225 --> 27:10.760
CAN YOU TELL ME I'LL SURVIVE
IF I GO THROUGH WITH THIS?

27:10.760 --> 27:11.931
HAVING THE PROCEDURE

27:11.931 --> 27:14.363
DOES NOT NECESSARILY IMPROVE
THE TREATMENT OUTCOME.

27:14.363 --> 27:16.065
YOU HAVE QUITE
THE BEDSIDE MANNER.

27:16.065 --> 27:18.367
YOU KNOW THAT, RIGHT?

27:18.367 --> 27:22.011
MY MOM DIED OF BREAST CANCER
WHEN SHE WAS IN HER 40s.

27:22.011 --> 27:24.043
I HAVE THAT CANCER GENE.

27:24.043 --> 27:26.015
MY CHANCES ARE
PRETTY MUCH LOSE-LOSE,

27:26.015 --> 27:28.017
WHICHEVER WAY
YOU LOOK AT IT,

27:28.017 --> 27:29.118
EXCEPT FOR THE BABY.

27:29.118 --> 27:30.950
WE'RE KEEPING IT.

27:32.021 --> 27:34.724
I'LL CALL DOWN
A PSYCH CONSULT.

27:34.724 --> 27:35.855
DON'T BOTHER.

27:35.855 --> 27:38.127
I AM GOING TO GET
FAT AND HAPPY

27:38.127 --> 27:40.229
INSTEAD OF SKINNY AND BALD.

27:40.229 --> 27:42.391
LOOK, IF YOU WANT TO LIVE --

27:42.391 --> 27:45.234
HONEY,
THAT'S WHAT I'M DOING.

27:59.008 --> 28:01.080
LOOK, IF YOU THINK
YOU'RE GONNA GET ANY,

28:01.080 --> 28:02.882
THINK AGAIN.

28:02.882 --> 28:05.214
I'M NOT IN THE MOOD.

28:05.214 --> 28:06.385
I'M NOT IN THE MOOD.

28:06.385 --> 28:08.788
GOOD.

28:12.121 --> 28:13.863
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

28:13.863 --> 28:14.924
NOTHING.

28:14.924 --> 28:17.026
I JUST HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
ALL DAY.

28:18.728 --> 28:21.270
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
SO, I'M WORKING.

28:27.036 --> 28:30.279
I'VE NEVER DONE
A BOVINE REPLACEMENT BEFORE.

28:30.279 --> 28:33.142
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I'M DOING.

28:33.142 --> 28:35.714
LOOK IT UP, RESEARCH IT,

28:35.714 --> 28:37.446
AND GET SOMEONE
TO ASSIST YOU.

28:37.446 --> 28:38.888
[ SCOFFS ]

28:38.888 --> 28:40.920
IT'S NOT THAT EASY.

28:40.920 --> 28:44.093
THIS IS A PROBLEM
THAT HAS A SOLUTION, BURKE.

28:44.093 --> 28:46.325
THERE ARE A LOT
OF PROBLEMS THAT DON'T.

28:51.060 --> 28:52.001
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

28:52.001 --> 28:54.834
THIRD THORACIC LAMINAE.
NOTHING.

28:54.834 --> 28:57.106
I THINK I SEE THE DURA
PULSATING HERE.

28:57.106 --> 28:59.168
NO, IT'S NOT.
KEEP LOOKING.

28:59.168 --> 29:01.040
WE HAVE BEEN AT THIS
FOR 4 HOURS.

29:01.040 --> 29:03.042
MAYBE HE JUST INJURED
HIS SPINAL CORD,

29:03.042 --> 29:04.243
AND THERE'S NOTHING TO FIX.

29:04.243 --> 29:06.015
GREY, WHEN YOU READ
YOUR BOOKS,

29:06.015 --> 29:07.947
MAKE SURE YOU REFERENCE THEM
CORRECTLY.

29:07.947 --> 29:10.519
PROGRESSIVE PARALYSIS
IMPLIES A PRESSURE LESION.

29:10.519 --> 29:12.221
MY BOOKS GOT ME HERE...

29:12.221 --> 29:14.123
[ MACHINE BEEPING ]

29:14.123 --> 29:17.186
PRESSURE'S 180 OVER 111.
THE PULSE IS IN THE 40s.

29:17.186 --> 29:18.427
WHAT IS IT?

29:18.427 --> 29:20.389
I'M PUSHING 70 MILLIGRAMS
OF DIAZOXIDE.

29:20.389 --> 29:22.431
OKAY.
AUTONOMIC DYSREFLEXIA.

29:22.431 --> 29:24.994
DAMAGE TO THE SYMPATHETIC
NERVOUS SYSTEM?

29:24.994 --> 29:26.966
B.P. AND THE HEART RATE
ARE UNSTABLE.

29:26.966 --> 29:27.967
WE'RE IN TROUBLE,
AREN'T WE?

29:27.967 --> 29:29.268
WE'VE GOT TO FIND THE CLOT.

29:35.004 --> 29:37.276
I CAN SEE THE CORD
BELOW THE DURA.

29:37.276 --> 29:39.408
FOCUS, GREY.
WE'RE GONNA FIND THE CLOT.

29:39.408 --> 29:40.509
IT'S THERE.

29:40.509 --> 29:42.111
CLEANUP, PLEASE.

29:42.111 --> 29:43.452
OKAY.

29:43.452 --> 29:45.454
B.P.'s STILL UP.
HEART RATE'S AT 44.

29:45.454 --> 29:47.116
GET ON THOSE BLEEDERS.

29:51.220 --> 29:53.122
KEEP LOOKING, DR. GREY.

29:55.164 --> 29:56.866
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

29:58.968 --> 29:59.969
DR. O'MALLEY?

29:59.969 --> 30:01.370
OUR PATIENT'S PULSE OX
IS DROPPING.

30:01.370 --> 30:03.372
SHE'S AGONAL.
SHE NEEDS TO BE INTUBATED.

30:03.372 --> 30:05.374
ISN'T THERE ANYONE ELSE
WHO CAN DO THIS?

30:05.374 --> 30:08.037
YOU'RE STANDING HERE.
I COULD TRY AND FIND SOMEONE.

30:08.037 --> 30:10.809
NO, THAT'S -- I GOT IT.

30:17.246 --> 30:18.487
OKAY.

30:18.487 --> 30:20.219
SATS DOWN TO 86%.

30:20.219 --> 30:21.290
CRICH PRESSURE, PLEASE.

30:22.892 --> 30:25.554
OKAY. I SEE CORDS.

30:25.554 --> 30:28.197
TUBE. HURRY.

30:38.237 --> 30:41.310
CHECK FOR BREATH SOUNDS.

30:46.515 --> 30:47.576
CLEAR AND EQUAL.

30:47.576 --> 30:50.449
C-O-2 DETECTOR
MELLOW YELLOW.

30:50.449 --> 30:52.952
SMOOTH MOVES, DOCTOR.

30:52.952 --> 30:56.155
KICKED ASS.

30:56.155 --> 30:58.057
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:58.057 --> 31:00.289
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:08.067 --> 31:10.499
OH, DR. KAREV.

31:10.499 --> 31:13.072
HOW LONG WOULD IT TAKE
TO GET A COW VALVE?

31:13.072 --> 31:15.474
ABOUT 60 MINUTES BY
MESSENGER.

31:18.547 --> 31:20.249
YOU'RE SCRUBBING IN.

31:20.249 --> 31:22.511
THANK YOU VERY MUCH, SIR.

31:22.511 --> 31:24.984
THIS DOESN'T GET YOU
ANY POINTS, KAREV.

31:24.984 --> 31:26.986
I'M THE ONLY ONE WITH POINTS
AROUND HERE.

31:29.318 --> 31:31.120
OH, BY THE WAY,

31:31.120 --> 31:33.923
DEVO WANTS A RABBI
TO BLESS HER BEFORE SURGERY.

31:33.923 --> 31:35.494
SERIOUSLY?

31:35.494 --> 31:37.066
YOU CAME UP WITH THE COW,

31:37.066 --> 31:38.467
YOU CAN FIND THAT GIRL
A RABBI.

31:41.931 --> 31:44.373
FOR THE IRRIGATION
AND SUCTION.

31:44.373 --> 31:46.275
RIGHT AWAY.

31:47.636 --> 31:50.009
WHAT IS IT?

31:50.009 --> 31:54.113
SEE FOR YOURSELF --
THE SECOND THORACIC VERTEBRAE.

31:56.285 --> 31:57.486
OH, MY GOD.

31:57.486 --> 32:00.289
I SEE IT.
IT REALLY IS THERE.

32:00.289 --> 32:01.550
OF COURSE IT IS.

32:01.550 --> 32:04.593
LET'S SUCTION AND PACK
THIS BABY, SHALL WE?

32:09.298 --> 32:10.229
THERE YOU GO.

32:10.229 --> 32:12.301
Woman:
Dr. Burke to Oncology.

32:12.301 --> 32:14.533
YOU WERE RIGHT.

32:14.533 --> 32:16.135
IS HE GONNA BE OKAY?

32:16.135 --> 32:17.136
I THINK SO.

32:17.136 --> 32:18.367
BUT YOU DON'T KNOW THAT.

32:18.367 --> 32:21.110
WE STOPPED THE PARALYSIS
FROM ADVANCING.

32:21.110 --> 32:22.411
BUT YOU DON'T KNOW
IF THE PARALYSIS

32:22.411 --> 32:24.013
HE ALREADY HAS
WILL BE PERMANENT.

32:24.013 --> 32:25.174
NO.

32:25.174 --> 32:28.347
YOU KEEP TAKING EVERYTHING
ON FAITH.

32:28.347 --> 32:30.649
HOW DO YOU KNOW
WHAT'S REAL AND WHAT'S NOT?

32:30.649 --> 32:32.281
YOU JUST DO.

32:33.422 --> 32:37.326
SOME PEOPLE WOULD CALL THIS
A RELATIONSHIP.

32:37.326 --> 32:39.228
THE KIND WHERE YOU
EXCHANGE KEYS,

32:39.228 --> 32:40.489
LEAVE YOUR TOOTHBRUSH OVER.

32:40.489 --> 32:43.332
WHO?
WHO WOULD CALL IT THAT?

32:43.332 --> 32:46.095
ME.

32:46.095 --> 32:49.298
I WOULD.

32:49.298 --> 32:50.639
I'M SUPPOSED TO BELIEVE YOU?

32:50.639 --> 32:51.970
UH-HUH.

32:51.970 --> 32:53.272
SHOW ME SOMETHING.

32:53.272 --> 32:55.244
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

32:55.244 --> 32:58.177
GIVE ME A REASON
TO BELIEVE.

