33:08.487 --> 33:10.989
â™ª TO ALL THE SAME OLD... â™ª

33:10.989 --> 33:13.192
I HAVE YOUR
DISCHARGE PAPERS.

33:13.192 --> 33:15.624
OH, YOU'RE NOT HAPPY
WITH ME, ARE YOU?

33:15.624 --> 33:17.996
I'M YOUR DOCTOR. IT'S NOT
MY PLACE TO BE HAPPY.

33:17.996 --> 33:20.299
MY HUSBAND AND CHILD
ARE GOING TO BE TOGETHER

33:20.299 --> 33:22.271
LONG AFTER I'M GONE.

33:22.271 --> 33:23.432
WE'VE TALKED ABOUT IT.

33:23.432 --> 33:26.275
IT'S OUR DECISION,
AND THAT'S OKAY.

33:26.275 --> 33:27.736
SO, WHY DO YOU NEED
MY APPROVAL?

33:27.736 --> 33:29.438
I WANT YOU TO UNDERSTAND.

33:29.438 --> 33:31.340
WELL, I DON'T.

33:35.084 --> 33:36.185
[ THUNDER RUMBLES ]

33:36.185 --> 33:37.546
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

33:42.721 --> 33:45.424
â™ª WASTE ALL DAY â™ª

33:45.424 --> 33:47.426
I BROUGHT
THE CONSENT FORMS AGAIN.

33:47.426 --> 33:49.458
YOU REALLY NEED
TO SIGN THEM.

33:49.458 --> 33:51.630
YOUR SURGEON SCHEDULED
THE O.R.

33:51.630 --> 33:55.134
MR. DUFF,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

33:55.134 --> 33:57.306
ARE YOU HAVING
ANOTHER SEIZURE?

33:59.568 --> 34:00.709
YEAH.

34:00.709 --> 34:02.441
YEAH. [ CLEARS THROAT ]

34:02.441 --> 34:04.113
I THINK MAYBE I AM.

34:06.245 --> 34:08.347
WHAT IS IT?

34:08.347 --> 34:12.781
â™ª HOW CAN I SEE
WHEN I AM BLIND? â™ª

34:12.781 --> 34:14.483
IT'S ME.

34:16.525 --> 34:18.657
I THINK IT'S ABOUT
TO BE OVER.

34:18.657 --> 34:22.391
WE KNOW WHAT WE'RE DOING,
MR. DUFF.

34:22.391 --> 34:24.093
YOU SAW THE ANGIO RESULTS.

34:24.093 --> 34:25.834
WE'RE CATCHING THE A.V.M.
JUST IN TIME.

34:25.834 --> 34:27.496
YOU DON'T NEED
TO BE NERVOUS.

34:27.496 --> 34:28.537
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DIE.

34:28.537 --> 34:31.670
I'M NOT TALKING ABOUT DYING.

34:31.670 --> 34:37.746
â™ª I CAN'T HOLD ON TO A LIFE â™ª

34:37.746 --> 34:40.679
MY WHOLE LIFE
HAS BEEN ABOUT WHAT I SEE

34:40.679 --> 34:43.782
AND ABOUT BELIEVING IN MYSELF,
WHATEVER PEOPLE THINK.

34:43.782 --> 34:48.157
YOU'RE TELLING ME THERE'S
A CHANCE THAT WILL GO AWAY.

34:48.157 --> 34:50.459
LOOK, YOU'RE A HEALTHY GUY.

34:50.459 --> 34:52.821
YOU'RE GONNA LIVE
A LONG, FULL LIFE.

34:52.821 --> 34:54.763
IF YOUR PSYCHIC VISIONS
ARE REAL,

34:54.763 --> 34:56.665
YOU'VE GOT TO BELIEVE
YOU'LL HAVE THEM

34:56.665 --> 34:58.667
WHEN YOU COME OUT.

35:03.432 --> 35:07.476
