[ THUNDER RUMBLES ]

35:16.715 --> 35:21.420
â™ª I'M UNDER NO ILLUSIONS NOW â™ª

35:23.492 --> 35:27.856
â™ª I'M UNDER NO ILLUSIONS NOW â™ª

35:35.564 --> 35:39.908
[ PRAYING IN HEBREW ]

36:03.532 --> 36:05.364
SHE'S GOOD.

36:05.364 --> 36:08.437
THIS IS DR. CHESNEY
FROM THE CLEVELAND CLINIC.

36:08.437 --> 36:12.841
HE'S AN EXPERT ON BOVINE
VALVE REPLACEMENT SURGERY.

36:12.841 --> 36:16.345
HE WILL BE ASSISTING
VIA SATELLITE.

36:16.345 --> 36:18.176
Thank you, Doctor.

36:18.176 --> 36:22.511
After the sternotomy
and connection to bypass,

36:22.511 --> 36:24.883
we're going to do
a transverse left atriotomy

36:24.883 --> 36:27.356
to expose the valve.

36:27.356 --> 36:29.958
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

36:38.567 --> 36:42.571
I TRIED TO TALK SHEPHERD OUT
OF THAT CLOT SURGERY.

36:42.571 --> 36:43.972
WHAT IS WRONG WITH ME?

36:43.972 --> 36:45.834
BASICALLY, YOU TRIED
TO KILL THE GUY.

36:45.834 --> 36:47.576
BASICALLY, YOU'RE AN ASS.

36:47.576 --> 36:48.837
YOU KNOW YOU WANT IT.

36:48.837 --> 36:51.510
COME TO PAPA, BABY.

36:51.510 --> 36:52.841
THIS, UH, IS GEORGE.

36:52.841 --> 36:56.385
GEORGE HAS A HOT DATE.

36:56.385 --> 36:57.616
[ LAUGHS ]

36:57.616 --> 36:59.217
OH, THAT'S GREAT, GEORGE.

36:59.217 --> 37:01.850
YEAH.

37:01.850 --> 37:04.222
LEFT POCKET OF MY LAB COAT,
GEORGIE.

37:04.222 --> 37:07.426
NO GLOVE, NO LOVE.

37:16.935 --> 37:19.237
[ INHALES, EXHALES DEEPLY ]

37:19.237 --> 37:20.409
MY PSYCHIC HAD HIS SURGERY.

37:20.409 --> 37:22.911
YEAH?

37:22.911 --> 37:26.014
I WONDER WHAT HAPPENED
WITH HIS...GIFT.

37:26.014 --> 37:28.016
COME ON.
WE ALL KNOW HE'S CRAZY.

37:28.016 --> 37:30.419
YOU SAID YOU DIDN'T BELIEVE
IN THAT STUFF.

37:33.852 --> 37:35.524
I GREW UP IN A TRAILER PARK.

37:35.524 --> 37:36.755
I WAITED TABLES,

37:36.755 --> 37:39.728
WHICH WAS SUPPOSED TO
PUT ME THROUGH COLLEGE,

37:39.728 --> 37:45.594
BUT MY MOTHER WAS ALWAYS CALLING
THESE PSYCHICS ALL THE TIME.

37:45.594 --> 37:47.436
AND THE BILLS STARTED PILING UP,

37:47.436 --> 37:49.338
SO I HAD TO USE MY MONEY
TO PAY THEM.

37:49.338 --> 37:51.900
WHEN I TURNED 18,
I LEFT AND NEVER WENT BACK.

37:51.900 --> 37:55.003
BUT THIS GUY HAS BEEN
SAYING THINGS TO ME --

37:55.003 --> 37:59.007
THINGS HE COULDN'T POSSIBLY
KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT.

37:59.007 --> 38:02.411
SO...I JUST WONDER.

38:05.514 --> 38:08.286
DO YOU HAVE SENSATION
ANYWHERE ELSE?

38:08.286 --> 38:10.859
SOME FEELING IN MY STOMACH
AND FEET, I GUESS.

38:10.859 --> 38:12.491
BLADDER AND BOWELS?

38:12.491 --> 38:13.922
NOT SO GOOD STILL.

38:13.922 --> 38:16.765
THE PRESSURE STOCKINGS
HELP RELIEVE CLOTS?

38:16.765 --> 38:18.026
THEY DO.

38:28.637 --> 38:29.978
I WANTED TO THANK YOU...

38:29.978 --> 38:31.810
FOR EVERYTHING.

38:31.810 --> 38:34.312
BELIEVING IN ME,
THAT I WASN'T MAKING IT UP.

38:35.784 --> 38:38.387
WELL, I'LL COME BACK
TOMORROW, THEN.

38:38.387 --> 38:40.789
I WANTED TO SHOW
YOU SOMETHING.

38:40.789 --> 38:43.792
I WASN'T SURE IT WOULD LAST,
BUT NOW LOOK.

38:47.325 --> 38:48.857
I KNOW IT'S HARDLY ANYTHING,
BUT --

38:48.857 --> 38:52.801
NO, IT'S SOMETHING.

38:52.801 --> 38:54.032
IT'S SOMETHING REALLY BIG.

38:54.032 --> 38:55.404
â™ª WHAT DO I â™ª

38:55.404 --> 38:57.706
â™ª WHAT DO I â™ª

38:57.706 --> 39:00.038
â™ª WHAT DO I NEED TO DO â™ª

39:00.038 --> 39:04.743
AT THE END OF THE DAY,
FAITH IS A FUNNY THING.

39:06.114 --> 39:09.718
IT TURNS UP WHEN
YOU DON'T REALLY EXPECT IT.

39:09.718 --> 39:13.021
MR. DUFF,
YOU'RE STILL WITH US.

39:15.023 --> 39:17.085
FOR YOUR RECIPE...

39:19.127 --> 39:23.061
ONE TABLESPOON
COCONUT EXTRACT.

39:24.833 --> 39:29.067
IT'S LIKE ONE DAY YOU REALIZE
THAT THE FAIRY TALE

39:29.067 --> 39:31.670
MAY BE SLIGHTLY DIFFERENT
THAN YOU DREAMED.

